data.description: THIS IS IT!! This ADORABLE three bedroom, one-and-a-half bathroom home walking distance to downtown Thomaston has a BRAND NEW kitchen and a FANTASTIC floorplan!! With a separate kitchen and dining room, this home offers space to breathe and relax. You won't BELIEVE the amount of closet space in this beautiful home! This sweet home is very close to Upson Regional Medical Center and convenient to the schools. The large kitchen has just been upgraded with brand new cabinets, countertops, paint, and vinyl plank flooring. The carport and private backyard offer the perfect outdoor space. This four-sided brick home is just LOVELY and is ready for you to move right in and make it your own!
